		<description><![CDATA[Jane found a very interesting article about the smallest village in Italy, and when we saw a few pictures of this tiny little place, we totally fell in love with it and we knew we had to share this story with you. So, let&#8217;s talk about &#8220;il villaggio piu&#8217; piccolo d&#8217;Italia&#8221; (the smallest village in [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="http://www.learnitalianpod.com/wp-content/imgs/bg-flag.gif" alt="LearnItalianPod" /> Jane found a very interesting article about the smallest village in Italy, and when we saw a few pictures of this tiny little place, we totally fell in love with it and we knew we had to share this story with you. So, let&#8217;s talk about &#8220;il villaggio piu&#8217; piccolo d&#8217;Italia&#8221; (the smallest village in Italy) all while learning how to use the superlative adjective plus some common Italian words and expressions that you can use to improve your Italian. Enjoy! </p>
