			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="http://www.learnitalianpod.com/wp-content/imgs/bg-flag.gif" alt="LearnItalianPod" />Learn Italian with www.LearnItalianPod.com &#8211;  Episode #18 of the fun-to-practice and extra-useful &#8220;Listen Up &#038; Learn&#8221; lesson series is entitled &#8220;Thank You For Calling&#8221; &#8211; It&#8217;s just past lunchtime and you decide to kick-start the afternoon with some shopping, determined to buy those great Italian shoes you saw the other day. So, you call the store and&#8230; surprise: the store is closed, and the answering machine is on. I bet you didn&#8217;t know that in Italy the majority of stores close for lunch, didn&#8217;t you!</p>
