<p>So, let&#8217;s have a lot of fun by listening and practicing some of the most famous movie lines ever, but&#8230; the way Italians heard them and love them. &#8211; The seven worldwide famous movie lines you&#8217;re about to hear will greatly improve your vocabulary, comprehension of Italian, and understanding of Italian culture. Enjoy!</p>
