<p> So, let&#8217;s get the phone ringing and practice two great, &#8220;real-life&#8221; phone conversations in Italian. The two phone conversations you&#8217;re about to hear, one informal and the other formal, will greatly improve your vocabulary, comprehension of Italian, and understanding of Italian culture. Enjoy!</p>
