<p>Here&#8217;s the question: &#8220;e&#8217; nato prima l&#8217;uovo o la gallina?&#8221; (in English: &#8220;which came first, the egg or the hen?&#8221;). A team of scientists seems to have found the answer to this challenging question, and we are going to share the news with you. </p>
