			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="http://www.learnitalianpod.com/wp-content/imgs/bg-flag.gif" alt="LearnItalianPod" />Learn Italian with the newest show on LearnItalianPod.com: &#8220;5 Minutes A Day&#8221;, episode #2! &#8220;5 Minutes A Day&#8221; lessons are &#8220;fun-to-listen-to&#8221; and &#8220;fun-to-practice&#8221; 5 to 10 minutes lessons that will provide you with knowledge on a great variety of topics and they are great for beginner, intermediate, and upper intermediate students of Italian. </p>
<p>On this second episode, we are going on a &#8220;white week&#8221; (settimana bianca), which means &#8220;going on a ski-holiday, going to the mountains&#8221;. Italians love to take their &#8220;settimana bianca&#8221; in January or February. You will get the chance to practice and improve your pronunciation and learn some interesting grammatical and cultural facts about this topic. Enjoy!</p>
