So today, let&#8217;s follow our friend Lucia as she calls ACI, the Italian roadside assistance, after her car suddenly stopped working, and let&#8217;s learn a lot of useful Italian that everyone can use in the unfortunate case of a car breakdown while in Italy. Enjoy! 
