<p>Considering Italy&#8217;s unemployment rates, this is definitely a desirable prize for someone unemployed, so no wonder the lottery is having a huge success! Let&#8217;s dedicate today&#8217;s Culture Shot to another unusual masterpiece of Italian creativity: &#8220;the job lottery&#8221;. Enjoy!</p>
