<p>You said it, Lisa, Italians can surely be resourceful, and what an example you brought up! So here it is, a Culture Shot about banks, loans, Parmesan cheese, and, most important, about the worldwide famous &#8220;arte di arrangiarsi italiana&#8221; (the Italian art of going with the flow). Enjoy!</p>
