<p>Presented at the Festival di Sanremo contest in 1962 by great singer and music producer Tony Renis, &#8220;Quando, Quando, Quando&#8221; didn&#8217;t win the contest, but went on to become a huge success all over the world, recorded by hundreds of different artists. The sung Italian of this great song is so clear and precise that you are sure to greatly improve your Italian pronunciation by practicing these lyrics. Happy singing, everyone! </p>
