<p>Excellent idea, Carlo! So, let&#8217;s practice the pronunciation of some of the difficult sounds of the Italian language, like &#8220;GL&#8221;, &#8220;GN&#8221;, and &#8220;SC&#8221;. And yes, we are going to practice these sounds with the help of some good old tongue twisters! &#8211; Oh, by the way, all of these tongue twisters are used in Italian schools to teach Italian to Italian kids, so&#8230; they work! </p>
