		<title>3. Can We Reschedule? (Upper Intermediate)</title>
		<link>http://www.learnitalianpod.com/2008/12/02/3-can-we-reschedule-upper-intermediate/</link>
		<comments>http://www.learnitalianpod.com/2008/12/02/3-can-we-reschedule-upper-intermediate/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Dec 2008 05:38:41 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>LearnItalianPod.com</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Upper Intermediate]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[phone]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[verbs]]></category>

