			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="http://www.learnitalianpod.com/wp-content/imgs/bg-flag.gif" alt="LearnItalianPod" />Learn Italian with LearnItalianPod! This episode is about&#8230; winning the &#8220;SuperEnalotto jackpot&#8221; and become a legend! The SuperEnalotto is the Italian lottery, and that&#8217;s what 99% of Italians are thinking about this week as a record-breaking prize of one hundred million euros (more or less 140 million US dollars), is up for grabs! They say the fever for the game is so high in Italy that the Italian consumer rights group is demanding that the record jackpot for the popular game be seized because it is &#8220;too high&#8221;. &#8211; So, let&#8217;s learn a thing or two about this &#8220;SuperEnalotto&#8217;s Fever&#8221;, and let&#8217;s see what Italians do to &#8220;hit the jackpot&#8221; and change their lives forever!</p>
