So, let&#8217;s learn and practice a selection of super-common, useful, and &#8220;fun to learn&#8221; idiomatic sentences that, once you master them, they will really make you sound like a real 100% Italian! Italian idiomatic sentences are expressions that usually cannot be literally translated in English but are really important to learn. In fact, they are what makes the Italian language so colorful and charming. Enjoy!</itunes:summary>
